WEBVTT

1
00:00:12.990 --> 00:00:15.660
TOMB RAIDER KING

2
00:01:30.460 --> 00:01:32.460
Die. you bastard!

3
00:01:41.870 --> 00:01:45.377
EPISODE 2: THE ONE THAT WILL BECOME
THE KING OF RELICS

4
00:01:45.460 --> 00:01:46.630
Boss!

5
00:01:49.680 --> 00:01:51.550
This belongs to me now.

6
00:01:52.080 --> 00:01:53.890
My blade!

7
00:01:55.070 --> 00:01:56.720
You see...

8
00:01:57.330 --> 00:01:59.060
This is how you use this thing.

9
00:02:06.510 --> 00:02:07.270
Hey!

10
00:02:13.240 --> 00:02:15.040
Die!

11
00:02:26.960 --> 00:02:29.547
He really stabbed us!

12
00:02:29.630 --> 00:02:32.130
Well? Still up for it?

13
00:02:40.430 --> 00:02:42.347
XIANG GALLERY
What did you just say?!

14
00:02:42.430 --> 00:02:45.857
You guys got your ass beat
by Seo Joo-Heon?! What?

15
00:02:45.940 --> 00:02:49.357
Did you think that was going
to be a reasonable excuse?!

16
00:02:49.440 --> 00:02:53.647
He suddenly got faster!

17
00:02:53.730 --> 00:02:55.577
Like he was a different person!

18
00:02:55.660 --> 00:02:57.637
I could tell just by
the colour of his eyes!

19
00:02:57.720 --> 00:03:00.077
So. how much did he take from you?

20
00:03:00.160 --> 00:03:05.217
Uh. all the money from the account.
and the Buddha statue...

21
00:03:05.300 --> 00:03:06.697
Huh?!

22
00:03:06.780 --> 00:03:08.977
What are you doing?!

23
00:03:09.060 --> 00:03:12.030
Take it back from him right now!

24
00:03:17.280 --> 00:03:18.717
That's strange...

25
00:03:18.800 --> 00:03:21.167
It's the same at other stores. too.

26
00:03:21.250 --> 00:03:24.640
It's not even worth 50.000 won.
I'd throw it away.

27
00:03:26.900 --> 00:03:31.840
Park was so flustered about it.
No way this is a cheap knockoff.

28
00:03:33.030 --> 00:03:34.457
SPY SKILL ACTIVATED

29
00:03:34.540 --> 00:03:36.447
DETECTED A SUSPICIOUS SUBSTANCE INSIDE THE STATUE
Suspicious substance?

30
00:03:36.530 --> 00:03:38.340
Inside?

31
00:03:43.620 --> 00:03:45.540
I see now.

32
00:03:59.200 --> 00:04:00.720
Knew it.

33
00:04:02.020 --> 00:04:04.970
It wasn't the kind of thing
you'd sell to a pawn shop.

34
00:04:06.930 --> 00:04:07.727
Oh. Joo-Heon.

35
00:04:07.810 --> 00:04:09.397
Hey. Mr. Geon-Woo. It's me.

36
00:04:09.480 --> 00:04:12.077
XIANG GALLERY

37
00:04:12.160 --> 00:04:13.317
XIANG GALLERY
Yes...

38
00:04:13.400 --> 00:04:15.087
Chairman...

39
00:04:15.170 --> 00:04:16.376
Yes.

40
00:04:16.459 --> 00:04:17.946
I'm sorry...

41
00:04:18.029 --> 00:04:19.029
Yes...

42
00:04:19.779 --> 00:04:21.529
Who's there? I'm on the phone here.

43
00:04:23.010 --> 00:04:24.617
Sis...

44
00:04:24.700 --> 00:04:27.957
We came here after receiving a tip about
drug smuggling and distribution.

45
00:04:28.040 --> 00:04:32.097
Drug? We're an art dealer here.

46
00:04:32.180 --> 00:04:34.050
We're upstanding citizens.

47
00:04:36.290 --> 00:04:38.217
All the evidence has been turned in.

48
00:04:38.300 --> 00:04:41.250
We hear the smuggled goods
are being stored in a warehouse.

49
00:04:41.520 --> 00:04:45.197
Why?! How does he know about
the warehouse in Gyeonggi?!

50
00:04:45.280 --> 00:04:48.980
But you need a passcode to get
into the storage room...

51
00:04:49.540 --> 00:04:54.027
A warehouse? Do you have proof?
Don't abuse your authority as police!

52
00:04:54.110 --> 00:04:56.610
600 pieces of artwork
confirmed at the warehouse.

53
00:04:57.470 --> 00:04:59.867
Drugs were found in all of them.

54
00:04:59.950 --> 00:05:00.777
What?!

55
00:05:00.860 --> 00:05:05.370
You opened all the storage rooms?!

56
00:05:06.140 --> 00:05:07.387
Just give it up.

57
00:05:07.470 --> 00:05:11.087
All of them have different passcodes...
This can't be happening.

58
00:05:11.170 --> 00:05:13.880
Hold it right there. Madam President.

59
00:05:14.820 --> 00:05:16.000
Here.

60
00:05:16.550 --> 00:05:20.297
Prez. this is what happens
when you don't live honestly.

61
00:05:20.380 --> 00:05:21.967
This voice... Seo Joo-Heon?!

62
00:05:22.050 --> 00:05:26.827
No matter how much of a hassle it is.
you have to change your passcode regularly.

63
00:05:26.910 --> 00:05:30.060
See you behind the bars.

64
00:05:31.060 --> 00:05:34.347
Damn you. Seo Joo-Heon!

65
00:05:34.430 --> 00:05:36.320
You'll remember this!

66
00:05:44.870 --> 00:05:45.947
MR. GEON-WOO
You should be receiving

67
00:05:46.030 --> 00:05:46.877
MR. GEON-WOO
100 million won as a reward.

68
00:05:46.960 --> 00:05:49.457
MR. GEON-WOO
Don't blow it in one go. Save the money. okay?

69
00:05:49.540 --> 00:05:51.787
MR. GEON-WOO
What a worrywart.

70
00:05:51.870 --> 00:05:54.587
Now that I've secured
the initial funds.

71
00:05:54.670 --> 00:05:56.877
I think I'll get some sleep at home.

72
00:05:56.960 --> 00:06:00.670
I guess I'll start looking for a tomb
in earnest starting tomorrow.

73
00:06:02.170 --> 00:06:03.300
Wha...

74
00:06:06.470 --> 00:06:09.180
I remember my home was here...

75
00:06:09.810 --> 00:06:12.290
A tomb just rose here?!

76
00:06:14.480 --> 00:06:17.620
I can't tell if this is good or bad luck.

77
00:06:23.650 --> 00:06:25.577
This is a real mess.

78
00:06:25.660 --> 00:06:27.617
What's going on?

79
00:06:27.700 --> 00:06:28.587
Are you okay?

80
00:06:28.670 --> 00:06:30.577
Yes. I just got here.

81
00:06:30.660 --> 00:06:32.620
Okay. get to it.

82
00:06:33.900 --> 00:06:37.587
The government here doesn't know
about the tombs yet. yes?

83
00:06:37.670 --> 00:06:40.027
The demolition will begin shortly.

84
00:06:40.110 --> 00:06:43.670
It seems no one has noticed the tomb yet.

85
00:06:44.190 --> 00:06:45.260
Excuse me.

86
00:06:46.140 --> 00:06:47.097
Hello.

87
00:06:47.180 --> 00:06:49.180
You...

88
00:06:50.000 --> 00:06:53.597
Don't be so surprised. Linda Walker.

89
00:06:53.680 --> 00:06:57.167
I wonder what the excavation team
from Japan is doing here.

90
00:06:57.250 --> 00:07:01.107
Big talk. coming from an American.

91
00:07:01.190 --> 00:07:03.157
Are you having jet lag?

92
00:07:03.240 --> 00:07:07.157
You sure are an eager thief. Abe Kiyoshi.

93
00:07:07.240 --> 00:07:11.057
We're all in the same boat. aren't we?
Don't act all high and mighty.

94
00:07:11.140 --> 00:07:14.417
If you let your guard down.
we'll take the relics for ourselves.

95
00:07:14.500 --> 00:07:15.937
Oh?

96
00:07:16.020 --> 00:07:20.747
A cunning agent from Langley.
and the stupid excavation team from Japan...

97
00:07:20.830 --> 00:07:22.857
So they're already here?

98
00:07:22.940 --> 00:07:27.517
Anyway. demolition? Judging by the fact that
they don't know how to handle tombs.

99
00:07:27.600 --> 00:07:30.027
there aren't any real experts here.

100
00:07:30.110 --> 00:07:31.010
Okay.

101
00:07:32.770 --> 00:07:35.470
Hey. this is...

102
00:07:38.020 --> 00:07:40.270
There's no doubt.
It's Tomb Glyphs.

103
00:07:42.060 --> 00:07:45.180
Tomb Glyphs. the language of relics.

104
00:07:45.820 --> 00:07:51.060
They're kind enough to write detailed
accounts of themselves all over the tombs.

105
00:07:52.700 --> 00:07:54.377
So if I read this.

106
00:07:54.460 --> 00:07:58.720
I'll know everything from the entrance
to the tomb to the location of the traps.

107
00:08:00.880 --> 00:08:03.880
Wow. what a great start.

108
00:08:06.380 --> 00:08:09.100
Time to read this.

109
00:08:10.890 --> 00:08:12.477
TITLE EXCEPTIONAL DECIPHERER UNLOCKED -
NEW SKILL OBTAINED

110
00:08:12.560 --> 00:08:13.537
TOMB RAIDER BASIC SKILLS

111
00:08:13.620 --> 00:08:14.847
LINGUISTIC RANK F ACTIVATED
That Crow bastard.

112
00:08:14.930 --> 00:08:17.390
TOMB RAIDER BASIC SKILLS (2/4)
How nice.

113
00:08:18.290 --> 00:08:22.700
Okay. I'll just have to activate
the remaining two. then.

114
00:08:25.630 --> 00:08:27.510
Is this the place?

115
00:08:30.910 --> 00:08:32.909
Time to head in.

116
00:08:54.130 --> 00:08:55.220
What the?!

117
00:08:57.300 --> 00:08:59.357
The tomb's entrance is opening!

118
00:08:59.440 --> 00:09:02.370
Say what?! The entrance is opening?!

119
00:09:09.490 --> 00:09:12.070
That's quite a dramatic way to open up.

120
00:09:13.090 --> 00:09:15.200
What's going on here?!

121
00:09:25.620 --> 00:09:29.800
It's about time I found something.

122
00:09:35.060 --> 00:09:36.420
All right.

123
00:09:37.380 --> 00:09:39.410
This should be the way.

124
00:09:48.530 --> 00:09:49.820
Found it.

125
00:10:04.110 --> 00:10:06.210
This should do it.

126
00:10:15.140 --> 00:10:17.790
Looks like we have a guest.

127
00:10:27.710 --> 00:10:33.917
How pitiful. Who dropped
something into this pond this time?

128
00:10:34.000 --> 00:10:36.240
Hey! Over here!

129
00:10:36.910 --> 00:10:38.930
Can't you see?

130
00:10:40.210 --> 00:10:42.700
What a slob.

131
00:10:46.220 --> 00:10:50.457
The golden sword and the silver sword.

132
00:10:50.540 --> 00:10:52.760
Which one did you drop?

133
00:10:53.660 --> 00:10:57.010
The relic here is The
Gold and Silver Axes.

134
00:10:57.820 --> 00:10:59.777
It's a very famous folktale.

135
00:10:59.860 --> 00:11:05.467
Based on "Mercury and the Woodcutter."
there are similar stories all over the place.

136
00:11:05.550 --> 00:11:09.087
I think anyone from any country
could easily clear this.

137
00:11:09.170 --> 00:11:12.150
But I'll be taking it this time.

138
00:11:12.910 --> 00:11:15.400
Now. choose quickly.

139
00:11:15.900 --> 00:11:19.410
Oh. boy. Neither is mine.

140
00:11:22.220 --> 00:11:24.557
What an honest man.

141
00:11:24.640 --> 00:11:29.170
Then is this yours?

142
00:11:31.810 --> 00:11:33.607
It's just like the template.

143
00:11:33.690 --> 00:11:35.807
If I say it's mine.

144
00:11:35.890 --> 00:11:40.397
I can get the gold and silver swords.
as well as this blade. and clear the trial.

145
00:11:40.480 --> 00:11:41.807
But...

146
00:11:41.890 --> 00:11:45.890
Can I confirm if that's really mine?

147
00:11:46.960 --> 00:11:49.400
Suit yourself.

148
00:11:56.480 --> 00:11:59.910
What are you doing?!

149
00:12:00.620 --> 00:12:02.910
Shut up! I don't trust you one bit!

150
00:12:04.110 --> 00:12:08.837
Just because I cleared the trial doesn't mean
there's any guarantee I'll get a reward.

151
00:12:08.920 --> 00:12:13.837
Besides. if I do get a reward. I might
end up being made into a murderer.

152
00:12:13.920 --> 00:12:17.847
How do you know about it?!

153
00:12:17.930 --> 00:12:20.257
The incident in America.

154
00:12:20.340 --> 00:12:22.587
SERIAL KILLING IN AMERICA
The Gold and Silver Axes have.

155
00:12:22.670 --> 00:12:24.337
ANOTHER CRIME BY A RELIC USER
at times. manipulated their owners

156
00:12:24.420 --> 00:12:27.720
ANOTHER CRIME BY A RELIC USER
and turned them into serial killers.

157
00:12:32.360 --> 00:12:35.860
Come at me! I'm taking you with me!

158
00:12:41.620 --> 00:12:43.990
Just accept your defeat!

159
00:12:45.840 --> 00:12:50.537
Do you really think you can
win me over with something like this?!

160
00:12:50.620 --> 00:12:52.647
I wonder how long you can hold out.

161
00:12:52.730 --> 00:12:55.280
I'll make you obey and submit
through my Dominance.

162
00:13:06.210 --> 00:13:07.217
Affinity.

163
00:13:07.300 --> 00:13:10.900
The ability to build a good relationship
with relics and work with them.

164
00:13:11.300 --> 00:13:12.367
Dominance.

165
00:13:12.450 --> 00:13:16.690
The ability to control relics and make them
obey commands through charisma.

166
00:13:17.280 --> 00:13:18.687
Adaptability.

167
00:13:18.770 --> 00:13:21.407
The depth of the connection
between a master and a relic

168
00:13:21.490 --> 00:13:25.160
For example. a musician's ability
to encounter a relic of an instrument.

169
00:13:40.140 --> 00:13:43.180
This one's a tough bastard!

170
00:13:48.270 --> 00:13:50.390
Get off me! Get off me!

171
00:13:51.570 --> 00:13:54.317
I'm definitely not going
to submit to the likes of you!

172
00:13:54.400 --> 00:13:58.647
I'm not going to use something
like Symbiosis in this life!

173
00:13:58.730 --> 00:14:00.907
Obey me!

174
00:14:00.990 --> 00:14:06.490
If you won't admit defeat.
I'll just have to destroy you.

175
00:14:07.040 --> 00:14:10.450
Hey. you hear me?!
Stop it!

176
00:14:31.760 --> 00:14:36.020
You're giving me a hard time.
Stop putting up a fight. will you?

177
00:14:43.630 --> 00:14:45.447
How gorgeous.

178
00:14:45.530 --> 00:14:46.667
TITLE THE ONE WHO EXPERIENCED
THE TOMB UNLOCKED - NEW SKILL OBTAINED

179
00:14:46.750 --> 00:14:48.717
TOMB RAIDER BASIC SKILLS -
TOMB EXCAVATION RANK F ACTIVATED

180
00:14:48.800 --> 00:14:51.457
TOMB EXCAVATION (RANK F) INCREASED
UNDERSTANDING OF TOMB

181
00:14:51.540 --> 00:14:56.447
Tomb Excavation skill?

182
00:14:56.530 --> 00:14:59.040
What should I do now?

183
00:15:02.550 --> 00:15:03.997
TITLE THE RELIC ABUSER UNLOCKED
The Relic Abuser?

184
00:15:04.080 --> 00:15:05.467
INCREASES DOMINANCE. DECREASES AFFINITY
The Relic Abuser?

185
00:15:05.550 --> 00:15:08.157
What? Abuser?

186
00:15:08.240 --> 00:15:13.487
That damn Crow...
Is he messing with me?!

187
00:15:13.570 --> 00:15:14.850
Here it is!

188
00:15:15.460 --> 00:15:17.350
Found it! It's the lake!

189
00:15:19.330 --> 00:15:21.780
Just as the prophecy said.

190
00:15:23.090 --> 00:15:26.110
Come out now. relic!

191
00:15:27.160 --> 00:15:29.160
What are you doing?!

192
00:15:29.650 --> 00:15:32.660
Fools. It's too late.

193
00:15:36.240 --> 00:15:38.170
Why isn't there any response?

194
00:15:38.670 --> 00:15:42.957
But the Prophet said.
"Throw a relic into the pond."

195
00:15:43.040 --> 00:15:44.170
Prophet?

196
00:15:44.720 --> 00:15:48.097
It seems there are people in Japan
who use the relics of prophecy.

197
00:15:48.180 --> 00:15:52.827
No. damn it! Don't pry. will you!

198
00:15:52.910 --> 00:15:54.430
What now?

199
00:15:55.150 --> 00:15:56.990
A quake!

200
00:16:01.940 --> 00:16:03.940
This is bad news!

201
00:16:06.420 --> 00:16:07.950
We gotta bail!

202
00:16:13.990 --> 00:16:15.517
XIANG GALLERY

203
00:16:15.600 --> 00:16:17.960
XIANG GALLERY
What the hell?

204
00:16:18.480 --> 00:16:21.377
They took everything.
not a single thing is left.

205
00:16:21.460 --> 00:16:25.887
Our president's been arrested...
Aren't we all totally out of work now?

206
00:16:25.970 --> 00:16:30.767
I know that! It's all Joo-Heon's fault!

207
00:16:30.850 --> 00:16:32.387
Unforgivable!

208
00:16:32.470 --> 00:16:34.517
I can't just sit here and keep quiet!

209
00:16:34.600 --> 00:16:39.767
That's my boss! You're going to put
Joo-Heon in his place. eh!

210
00:16:39.850 --> 00:16:42.957
Obviously! You've got
Mr. Oh Seug-Woo here!

211
00:16:43.040 --> 00:16:46.357
A man who always pays back
what he owes. a real man!

212
00:16:46.440 --> 00:16:48.867
Yeah!

213
00:16:48.950 --> 00:16:50.867
UNDERLING SEON JOO-HEON

214
00:16:50.950 --> 00:16:52.740
What?

215
00:17:11.359 --> 00:17:14.887
It's me. Hello?

216
00:17:14.970 --> 00:17:18.980
Why did it take you so long to answer?
You wanna die?

217
00:17:20.030 --> 00:17:22.667
You really don't know how to show
respect to your seniors!

218
00:17:22.750 --> 00:17:23.776
Shut up.

219
00:17:23.859 --> 00:17:27.329
I'll give you guys some work to do.

220
00:17:30.580 --> 00:17:33.517
What the hell...
Yes. mission failed.

221
00:17:33.600 --> 00:17:37.200
Huh? It had be prophesied?
What do you mean?

222
00:17:37.730 --> 00:17:41.377
We only found out later that a Korean
had already taken the initiative.

223
00:17:41.460 --> 00:17:45.537
Damn it! Why didn't you tell me
the most important information?!

224
00:17:45.620 --> 00:17:49.357
You know what kind of person is
the user of Future Guide. right?

225
00:17:49.440 --> 00:17:52.907
Don't tell me...
Kid can't read Kanji?!

226
00:17:52.990 --> 00:17:54.737
You just can't help kids these days.

227
00:17:54.820 --> 00:17:58.157
We'll be watching out as well.
so keep up the good work.

228
00:17:58.240 --> 00:18:01.857
Also. be careful of that Korean.

229
00:18:01.940 --> 00:18:03.900
Huh? What?

230
00:18:04.880 --> 00:18:07.200
An ominous prophecy has been made.

231
00:18:09.920 --> 00:18:12.987
The one who devours the world. it says.

232
00:18:13.070 --> 00:18:15.820
What?! Midas?!

233
00:18:16.320 --> 00:18:21.550
Midas is the world's largest secret auction.
held in Las Vegas.

234
00:18:22.720 --> 00:18:27.007
If I can sneak in there. I might be
able to find out what he's up to.

235
00:18:27.090 --> 00:18:29.787
Go to this month's regular auction

236
00:18:29.870 --> 00:18:34.507
and look for the items up for auction
and a person named JK. Jack Kayman.

237
00:18:34.590 --> 00:18:36.517
That's Kwon's alias.

238
00:18:36.600 --> 00:18:40.427
Don't be stupid!
How are we supposed to go there?!

239
00:18:40.510 --> 00:18:42.977
You figure it out.

240
00:18:43.060 --> 00:18:46.367
I'll pay you generously.
so don't worry about expenses.

241
00:18:46.450 --> 00:18:48.240
This is business.

242
00:18:50.140 --> 00:18:52.610
You guys choose.

243
00:18:53.060 --> 00:18:56.240
Obey me. or be beaten to death.

244
00:19:01.740 --> 00:19:03.500
Thank you.

245
00:19:06.250 --> 00:19:09.750
Well. I've got all the necessary
preparations done for now.

246
00:19:12.290 --> 00:19:15.677
Time for some relic hunting.
- Breaking news.

247
00:19:15.760 --> 00:19:19.170
This is the fourth random attack
to occur this month.

248
00:19:19.760 --> 00:19:21.407
SELF-IMMOLATION ATTEMPT
It is reported that the suspect.

249
00:19:21.490 --> 00:19:22.897
AT YEONGDEUNGPO STATION?
after behaving suspiciously.

250
00:19:22.980 --> 00:19:25.687
AT YEONGDEUNGPO STATION?
attempted to set himself on fire.

251
00:19:25.770 --> 00:19:27.217
Come to think of it.

252
00:19:27.300 --> 00:19:31.330
I do remember a lot of incidents like this
happening before the tombs appeared.

253
00:19:36.180 --> 00:19:38.617
